-- MOVES-Pimco names executive vice president
-- 
-- Tue Aug 05, 2014 12:02PM EDT
-- None



Aug 5 (Reuters) - Pacific Investment Management Company LLC (Pimco) hired Ethan Schwartz as executive vice president and portfolio manager focusing on distressed credit.

Prior to joining Pimco, Schwartz was senior analyst at Contrarian Capital Management where he managed a broad range of complex investments in liquid and illiquid fund structures. [ID:nMKWkhLV6a]